snippet.title: REKA Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Reka is an atmospheric home building game.

🐈‍⬛ Play as a wayfaring witch and explore the countryside. 
🌿  Collect ingredients, craft and aid lost souls. 
🐔 Build & decorate your own witches cottage! 

If you want to support us you can wishlist REKA on Steam!
http://bit.ly/RekaGame

https://twitter.com/emberstorm_de
reka.emberstorm.de 
https://emberstorm.de/press/
